programme.title: Även anglar ater bonor
programme.desc: Fribrottaren Charlie (Bud Spencer) och drommaren Sonny (Giuliano Gemma) ar två fattiga tuffingar i 30-talets Chicago som hoppas på battre tider. De får chansen till stora pengar nar de borjar arbeta for en maffiaboss. Problemet ar att de ar alldeles for blodiga. De lånar ut pengar till fattiga istallet for att inkassera beskyddarpengar och driver hela tiden maffiabossen till vansinne. Till slut beslutar sig skurkarna for att undanroja Charlie och Sonny. Men de har glomt en sak - Charlies formidabla styrka sitter framst i navarna!

programme.title: Gun
programme.desc: Vapenrelaterat våld och en skenande brottsstatistik får polisen i Detroit att tillsammans med FBI starta ett fullskaligt krig mot stadens vapensmugglare. Rich och hans organisation blir de framsta måltavlorna for operationen. Och då Rich, hans baste van Angel, och hans alskarinna och leverantor Gabriella råkar ut for en affarsuppgorelse som går fel, avslojas en stor hemlighet som skakar Rich anda in i margen. Det blir hogexplosiv action med bland annat Val Kilmer, Curtis ”50 Cent” Jackson och Danny Trejo!

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Det hela borjar med att en magisk spira transporterar deras goda van April genom tid och rum, anda till samurajernas Japan. Leonardo och ganget ger sig genast av efter henne, och måste nu besegra den elake Lord Naringa for att radda den insparrade April och återta spiran som lorden kommit over. Annars lar de bli fast i medeltida Japan i eviga tider. Och dar finns ju inte ens några pizzerior…

programme.title: Shockwave
programme.desc: Nar en massiv vulkanisk storm drabbar varlden forsoker geofysikern Kate Ferris overtyga forsvarsdepartementet att det inte ar ett naturligt fenomen. Det ar resultatet av ett seismiskt supervapen, kant som Hell Storm, som aktiverats. Kate måste komma på ett satt att stoppa chockvågen innan den hotar manskligheten.

programme.title: Joyride
programme.desc: Jon ar en forkrossad men andå charmig odugling i nastan allt han foretar sig, Luke ar en mastare på att kora bil och på flykt från sitt forflutna och Keira ar drive-thru-bitrade på ett burgerstalle och veganaktivist. Tillsammans bildar de tre en trio tillfalliga banditer nar de reser genom hela Nya Zeeland i en "lånad" gul Mini Cooper och ifrågasatter samhallets likriktning och jagar forlorad karlek med ett massivt polisuppbåd och varsta mediacirkusen hack i hal.

programme.title: Nerve
programme.desc: Skotsamma high school-tjejen Vee Delmonico ar less på att leva livet från åskådarplats. Hennes kompisar pressar henne till att borja spela det populara natspelet Nerve och Vee bestammer sig for att registrera sig for bara en enda utmaning och en stunds harmlos underhållning. Men hon dras med av spanningen och fastnar i det adrenalinpumpande spelet i sallskap med en mystisk framling och spelet blir allt laskigare med standigt farligare utmaningar som for henne mot en final med hoga insatser som kommer att avgora hela hennes framtid.

programme.title: Texas Red
programme.desc: Den sanna historien om legendariske Texas Red, en afroamerikansk man som vildsint jagades utmed prariens sargade landskap av hundratals laglosa cowboys genom Mississippis vintervildmark. Allt for att lagga beslag på den hogst eftertraktade beloningen.

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: Final Shot
programme.desc: Lonnmordaren Frank har lagt sitt tidigare arbete på hyllan och forsoker leva ett till synes vanligt liv tillsammans med flickvannen och hans dotter. En dag kommer en okand maffia boss forbi for att få Franks hjalp att ha ihjal den som tagit livet av hans unga dotter. For att inte dra in sin egen familj i eventuella komplikationer måste Frank fatta ett beslut om att gora stoten åt bossen eller få ro med sin egen sjal?

programme.title: Daredevil
programme.desc: Mot DAREDEVIL - Marvels legendariske superhjalte, kand som Mannen utan fruktan. Med spektakulara specialeffekter, slagsmålsscener utver det vanliga och nonstop action. programme.title: Raining in the Mountain
programme.desc: I ett buddhisttempel i Mingdynastins Kina ar det dags for abboten att utse sin eftertradare. Men bland kandidaterna finns det de som framst ar ute efter att stjala den ovarderliga skriften i templets skattkammare. Intriger och allianser uppstår nar personliga ambitioner och andliga stravanden kolliderar.

programme.title: Revenge
programme.desc: Richard tar med sin alskarinna Jen på lyxig jaktweekend med grabbarna. Efter en lång festnatt har hans ena kompis svårt att hålla fingrarna borta från Jen, och snart går allt overstyr. Skarrad efter våldtakten berattar Jen for en ointresserad Richard vad som hant. Hon hotar då med att beratta allt for hans fru, vilket istallet gor honom rasande och våldsam. Morbultad och blodig lamnar killarna Jen i oknen for att mota sitt ode, men hon ar inte redo att do. Hon ar redo for HÄMND!

programme.title: Skumma polare
programme.desc: Trinityseriens stjarna Bud Spencer återvander till vilda vastern i regissoren Michele Lupo’s komedi om bedragaren Buddy, som misstas for en lakare efter att hans van Cocoa oavsiktligt stjal en resvaska med kirurgiska instrument. Buddy bosatter sig i den lilla staden som en experimentell lakare. Nar ett gang våldsamma brottslingar forsoker ta over staden, visar det sig att hans sanna talang ar att slå ner skurkar synkad till musik som humoristiskt komponerats av spaghettivastmastaren Ennio Morricone.

programme.title: Saknad i strid (Missing in Action)
programme.desc: Amerikanska soldater hålls fångna i Vietnam — och det ar upp till en man att fora hem dem i denna fartfyllda action/aventyrsfilm med kampsportslegenden Chuck Norris. Efter en djarv flykt från ett krigsfånglager ar overste James Braddock (Norris) på ett uppdrag att lokalisera och radda saknade soldater med hjalp av en tjansteman från utrikesdepartementet (Lenore Kasdorf) och en tidigare armekompis (M. Emmet Walsh). Denna enmansarme ar redo att ta sig in i Vietnam… men kan han ta sig ut igen?

programme.title: Godsend
programme.desc: Efter deras unga sons dod kommer Paul och Jessie Duncan overens om att få honom klonad av en mystisk lakare. Saker och ting tar en olycksbådande vandning nar deras nya son vaxer upp och de lar sig en chockerande hemlighet om lakaren.

programme.title: Bulletproof Monk
programme.desc: The Monk ar en zen-cool martial arts-mastare vars uppgift har varit att beskydda en maktig antik skrift, en mystisk artefakt som bar nyckeln till obegransad makt. Nu har The Monk inlett sitt sokande efter skriftens naste vaktare, och uppdraget for honom till USA.

programme.title: Power Rangers
programme.desc: Fem helt vanliga high school-elever vaknar med helt fantastiska superkrafter efter att ha hittat ett gammalt rymdskepp. Nar de upptacker att deras lilla hemstad Angel Grove – hela varlden faktiskt – håller på att utplånas av aliens forstår de att odet har valt ut just dem till att radda planeten. For att uppfylla sitt ode som superhjaltar måste de forst overvinna sina personliga problem for att kunna forenas som POWER RANGERS.

programme.title: Spaghettiman
programme.desc: Clark saknar empati for allt och alla. Han skiter fullstandigt i varlden vi lever i och bryr sig knappt om sig sjalv heller. Men efter en incident med en gammal gryta fylld av spaghetti och en trasig mikro går nått fullstandigt snett. Clark forvandlas till en superhjalte som kan bekampa kriminalitet med hjalp av spaghetti. Men det finns en hake, du måste betala honom.

programme.title: Udda eller jamt
programme.desc: Polisen har misslyckats med att krossa ligan som svarar for den illegala spelverksamheten i Florida. Marinofficeren Johnny Firpo (Terence Hill) tar over uppdraget och raknar med hjalp av ex-spelaren Charlie Firpo (Bud Spencer). Det udda paret visar sig vara halvbroder, men Charlie vill andå inte hjalpa Johnny. Inte forran denne ljuger ihop en historia om att deras far ar blind och måste genomgå en dyr operation. Charlie inser att han måste tjana ihop till operationen genom ett antal poker- och spelvinster. Som vanligt får paret också många tillfallen att utnyttja sina stenhårda navar!

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Ghost Rider - Spirit Of Vengeance
programme.desc: Eld ska med eld bekampas! Johnny Blaze kampar alltjamt mot sin forbannelse som djavulens prisjagare. Och nar en hemlig religios sekt vill anlita hans tjanster, kanner han sig inte redo att annu en gång iklada sig Ghost Riders brinnande krafter och makt. Men kanske ar detta den sista mojligheten att gora sig fri från djavulens forbannelse en gång for alla!

programme.title: The Fourth Musketeer
programme.desc: På uppdrag av sin far reser den unge dArtagnan från landsbygden i Gascogne till Paris, dar han blir indragen i en listig och mycket komplicerad komplott mellan kungens musketorer och kardinal Richelieus gardister. Blod ska spillas, och den som inte ar på sin vakt kommer få satta livet till.

programme.title: Harsh Times
programme.desc: Fasansfulla mardrommar plågar fortfarande den f.d. soldaten Jim Davis som ar tillbaka i L.A. efter att ha varit utstationerad i Irak. Han ar saker på att ett jobb i LAPD skulle kunna jaga det forflutnas spoken på flykten, men nar han inte får jobbet fylls han av desperation. Och tillsammans med kompisen Mike dras Jim in i en brutal vardag praglad av våld, rån och missbruk i South Central, Los Angeles okanda gangkvarter.

programme.title: Hamburger Hill
programme.desc: Bravo Companys-man står infor en kamp som ar uppforsbacke... uppfor Hamburger Hill. Fjorton krigstrotta soldater kampar for en lera tackt jordhog som ar så namngiven, eftersom den tuggar upp soldater som hackat kott. De kampar for sitt land, sina medsoldater och sina liv. Krig ar helvete, men det har ar varre. Hamburger Hill berattar hur det var, som det verkligen var. Den ar en rå, modig och helt oforsonlig dramatisk skildring av en av de hårdaste striderna i Amerikas blodigaste krig. Detta hande. Hamburger Hill - krig nar den ar som varst, man då de ar som bast.

programme.title: Godsend
programme.desc: Efter deras unga sons dod kommer Paul och Jessie Duncan overens om att få honom klonad av en mystisk lakare. Saker och ting tar en olycksbådande vandning nar deras nya son vaxer upp och de lar sig en chockerande hemlighet om lakaren.

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: En forskare blir kidnappad och slangd ut i en dodsbringande oken dar hon måste kampa mot elementen for att overleva.

programme.title: Beak and Brain - Genius Birds from Down Under
programme.desc: These child prodigies of the animal kingdom have feathers and beaks – and very special skills! The Keas of New Zealand are the only parrots that live in snowy mountain areas. They like testing their brains, solving puzzles and challenging tourists: they unscrew bottle-tops, dismantle windscreen wiper blades and tear open rucksacks. They seem so determined you’d think they have an understanding of physics and mechanics! Thousands of miles northwards, in New Caledonia, other birds have talent, too. Here bird expert Gavin Hunt discovered that crows are able to produce a whole set of tools, each designed for a particular purpose – the most intricate tool culture in the animal kingdom! These...

programme.title: Wild Skagerrak
programme.desc: The strait that connects the North Sea with the Baltic, with depths of over 700 metres, is notorious for its dangerously strong currents. But currents also mean food and therefore nourishment for the large swarms of fish that inhabit the region. The sea grass meadows are comparable with those off the Californian coast. Harbour seals, grey seals and orcas hunt here, as do the rare black mouth cat shark and porpoises. Close by, catfish mate, which in itself is quite spectacular and never caught on film in this way before. Lions mane jellyfish with nettle threads of up to 30 metres in length make their way through the open sea. Skagerraks coastal regions are amongst the most beautiful and...

programme.title: Europes Wild River - The Elbe - 1.000 Miles of Wildlife and Nature
programme.desc: The river rises in the Czech Giant Mountains. Here it is called the Labe. After Děčín it flows into Germany and is called Elbe. There are various explanations for the origin of the river name "Elbe". One often mentioned is the Latin name of the river "albia", which means "bright water". This would also explain why the stream is referred to with the feminine article "the Elbe", since the Latin term "albia" is also feminine. Rather poetic than linguistically probable, however, is the explanation that elves (Middle High German: alb) scurrying around the pines in the white river mists could have helped the river to get its name. Geographically, the river can be divided into different...

programme.title: The Sudheide - Woods, meadows, open country
programme.desc: Forests and fields, moors and heathland, shepherds and sheep - these are the symbols of an ostensibly unspoilt landscape that has inspired poets and painters alike for centuries. The secret of the almost 500 km² nature reserve Naturpark Sudheide lies in its diversity: the origins of its soil, geology and topography can be traced back to the ice age. But the region between Hamburg and Hannover is anything but unspoilt. For centuries, it was synonymous with heathland farmers and formed as a North German cultivated landscape. This documentary tells of an almost unknown region, which has been strongly influenced by mankind for centuries, yet still remains diverse in its nature. Nature...

programme.title: Wild Alpine Rivers - Life in the Extreme
programme.desc: What would happen to the mountains without water? They would turn into deserts, devoid of life and vegetation. But there are very few mountains without water on our planet. They take care of this themselves, creating their life’s element and taking water directly from the sky by entrapping the clouds around them. This water then collects on the flanks of the mountains, where it turns from rivulets into rivers, that flow out into the oceans. Mountains and water are symbiotic, a cycle that keeps life on earth going. Mountain streams slowly move along meadows before, only moments later, turning into the spray of waterfalls or small mystic lakes. What kind of life can be found in and around...

programme.title: Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape: Episode 1
programme.desc: A few thousand years ago, there were bare moraine ridges and barren meltwater valleys here. A landscape born in the last ice age, characterized by the edge of the Alps, gentle hills, moors, and lakes. And by cultural richness, not only on the islands in Lake Chiemsee, with their famous monasteries and castles. Long before King Ludwig II, the first people settled in the Chiemgau region. Finds of hunting weapons from the Neanderthal era prove that the land was inhabited even during the ice age, probably because there was plenty of game to hunt. During the Bronze Age, one of the most important trade routes from the mountains to the Alpine foothills passed through here. Then came the Celts...

programme.title: Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape: Episode 2
programme.desc: Three times in the past two decades, the Chiemsee area has experienced "once-in-a-century" floods. Climate, wildlife, and landscape have changed, and it seems this transformation is accelerating. Species living in the flood zones are developing sophisticated survival strategies. Knot ants, for instance, place their queen in the middle and form a raft with their bodies, even conquering new habitats. Flooding is less of a disaster for nature and impacts humans more significantly.

programme.title: North Macedonia: Between Traditional Dances and Mini Navy
programme.desc: Northern Macedonia emerged from being a once constituent republic of the former Yugoslavia. Anyone wishing to discover unknown worlds has every chance of finding them in this young Balkan country, full of imposing mountains, lakes of crystal-clear water, original villages and centuries-old customs. Nevertheless, Northern Macedonia, which borders Serbia in the north and Greece in the south, considered to be one of the poorest countries in Europe.

programme.title: mareTV: The Blue and White Island World of Greece: Mykonos, Naxos and Tinos
programme.desc: Around the once sacred Isle of Delos, some 200 islands, including 20 larger ones, are arranged almost in a circle. This is where the name of the Greek island paradise comes from: Cyclades, a derivation of the Greek word kýklos, circle. Each cyclade has a unique character. The pelican Petros, about 20 years old, is the mascot of Mykonos. He moves from taverna to taverna all day long, scrounging fish. This works out sometimes well and sometimes not so well. Petros does have a few human friends who regularly slip him something, but all too often visitors eager to take pictures block his path. Then he has to "wiggle" his way through the crowd. Jackie Onassis is said to have once brought...

programme.title: The Green Heart of Croatia - At the Banks of River Sava
programme.desc: Every year, in the middle of Croatia, its the same story: after the annual snowmelt, a huge flood wave spills out of the Alps toward Zagreb and Belgrade. This leads to an increase in the River Savas water levels of some ten metres. The contents of more than ten billion bathtubs floods an area the size of Lake Constance, often for months on end, yet still the Croatian and Serbian capital is spared a flood disaster. One of the reasons for this is the fact that the Sava is able to flow unhindered. The annual floods not only create a natural retention reservoir for flood control: alongside the Sava lies a natural paradise, unique in Central Europe. In the species-rich, alluvial flood...

This leads to an increase in the River Savas water levels of some ten metres. The contents of more than ten billion bathtubs floods an area the size of Lake Constance, often for months on end, yet still the Croatian and Serbian capital is spared a flood disaster. One of the reasons for this is the fact that the Sava is able to flow unhindered. The annual floods not only create a natural retention reservoir for flood control: alongside the Sava lies a natural paradise, unique in Central Europe. In the species-rich, alluvial flood...

programme.title: Dream Islands Of Europe: Capri, Ischia and Procida
programme.desc: Capri and Ischia are world famous. From Naples, its just a short hop over to the two islands. Perfect destinations, then, for a weeks cruise along the Gulf of Naples and the adjoining Amalfi Coast to the south. There, Positano, Amalfi or Salerno as well as a handful of other mostly small harbor towns are extremely worthwhile destinations.

programme.title: mareTV: Venice - Lagoon and Legend
programme.desc: Venice has been attracting people as if by magic for centuries. The Italians call her La Serenissima, or the sublime. Perched on wooden posts, she braves the elements and the huge, annual surge of visitors. Vogalonga is the name of a Venetian sports competition for women, in which the participants row their boats standing. This is a tradition that Guilia and Elena also follow. They train hard, as the yearly regatta is soon to begin. Anyone caught driving their water vehicle with more than 7 km/h through the canals of Venice, risks getting a ticket from local policewoman Lorenza Mariutti. The reason: the resulting waves gnaw at the foundations of the grand palaces. Venetians are very...

programme.title: Italy My Love
programme.desc: In ten coastal areas of Italy, we encounter people that have a very special relationship with their region. All of them love their country, their traditions and their work. We met with enthusiasts and hedonists that permitted us to take a glimpse into their everyday lives. Young Italians, who have rediscovered nature and its treasures. Others, that preserve the beauty, archaeologists that apply whole new methods, farmers that only cultivate that which the soil needs. Fishermen, who fish in the same way as it was done a century ago and tough, young men who play and dance the Tarantella. Dolphins, giant sea turtles and pink flamingos, which are researched, nursed back to health or simply...

programme.title: Wild Sardinia
programme.desc: Sardinia has always been the epitome of pure wilderness, an emerald of volcanic origin in the Mediterranean. 1900 metres of coastline and an infinite maze of offshore islands. But Sardinia also has other facets: green valleys, rugged mountains, murmuring brooks, mysterious ruins and a unique fauna. Just off of Sardinias coast is an untouched underwater paradise - uniquely beautiful, but also dangerous. Pilot whales, dolphins and mobula rays populate the waters at Capo Testa in the north of the island. In the west, the lagoons of Cabras represent a wild landscape of lakes in which thousands of flamingos live and hunt the red brine shrimps. In addition to the flamingos, grey and purple...

programme.title: Wild Switzerland
programme.desc: Gentle, green meadows, rugged rock faces, mysterious lakes, dense forests, tall mountains, low-lying river deltas, quietly meandering mountain streams and smack dab in the middle, a unique fauna - THIS is Switzerland! We trace the elementary power of nature and present animals and plants in landscapes that have hardly ever been touched by mankind. Switzerland is an alpine country, but it is also Europes surge tank. Rivers such as the Rhine and the Rhone have their sources here. Glaciers, crevasses, icy cold caves and the underwater dome of the Verzasca are the unusual settings we chose for this film. We meet with rare, selected animal species and present their behavioural patterns, such...

programme.title: Wild Skagerrak
programme.desc: The strait that connects the North Sea with the Baltic, with depths of over 700 metres, is notorious for its dangerously strong currents. But currents also mean food and therefore nourishment for the large swarms of fish that inhabit the region. The sea grass meadows are comparable with those off the Californian coast. Harbour seals, grey seals and orcas hunt here, as do the rare black mouth cat shark and porpoises. Close by, catfish mate, which in itself is quite spectacular and never caught on film in this way before. Lions mane jellyfish with nettle threads of up to 30 metres in length make their way through the open sea. Skagerraks coastal regions are amongst the most beautiful and...

programme.title: Europes Wild River - The Elbe - 1.000 Miles of Wildlife and Nature
programme.desc: The river rises in the Czech Giant Mountains. Here it is called the Labe. After Děčín it flows into Germany and is called Elbe. There are various explanations for the origin of the river name "Elbe". One often mentioned is the Latin name of the river "albia", which means "bright water". This would also explain why the stream is referred to with the feminine article "the Elbe", since the Latin term "albia" is also feminine. Rather poetic than linguistically probable, however, is the explanation that elves (Middle High German: alb) scurrying around the pines in the white river mists could have helped the river to get its name. Geographically, the river can be divided into different...

programme.title: The Sudheide - Woods, meadows, open country
programme.desc: Forests and fields, moors and heathland, shepherds and sheep - these are the symbols of an ostensibly unspoilt landscape that has inspired poets and painters alike for centuries. The secret of the almost 500 km² nature reserve Naturpark Sudheide lies in its diversity: the origins of its soil, geology and topography can be traced back to the ice age. But the region between Hamburg and Hannover is anything but unspoilt. For centuries, it was synonymous with heathland farmers and formed as a North German cultivated landscape. This documentary tells of an almost unknown region, which has been strongly influenced by mankind for centuries, yet still remains diverse in its nature. Nature...

programme.title: Wild Alpine Rivers - Life in the Extreme
programme.desc: What would happen to the mountains without water? They would turn into deserts, devoid of life and vegetation. But there are very few mountains without water on our planet. They take care of this themselves, creating their life’s element and taking water directly from the sky by entrapping the clouds around them. This water then collects on the flanks of the mountains, where it turns from rivulets into rivers, that flow out into the oceans. Mountains and water are symbiotic, a cycle that keeps life on earth going. Mountain streams slowly move along meadows before, only moments later, turning into the spray of waterfalls or small mystic lakes. What kind of life can be found in and around...

programme.title: Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape: Episode 1
programme.desc: A few thousand years ago, there were bare moraine ridges and barren meltwater valleys here. A landscape born in the last ice age, characterized by the edge of the Alps, gentle hills, moors, and lakes. And by cultural richness, not only on the islands in Lake Chiemsee, with their famous monasteries and castles. Long before King Ludwig II, the first people settled in the Chiemgau region. Finds of hunting weapons from the Neanderthal era prove that the land was inhabited even during the ice age, probably because there was plenty of game to hunt. During the Bronze Age, one of the most important trade routes from the mountains to the Alpine foothills passed through here. Then came the Celts...

programme.title: Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Chiemgau, A Changing Landscape: Episode 2
programme.desc: Three times in the past two decades, the Chiemsee area has experienced "once-in-a-century" floods. Climate, wildlife, and landscape have changed, and it seems this transformation is accelerating. Species living in the flood zones are developing sophisticated survival strategies. Knot ants, for instance, place their queen in the middle and form a raft with their bodies, even conquering new habitats. Flooding is less of a disaster for nature and impacts humans more significantly.

programme.title: North Macedonia: Between Traditional Dances and Mini Navy
programme.desc: Northern Macedonia emerged from being a once constituent republic of the former Yugoslavia. Anyone wishing to discover unknown worlds has every chance of finding them in this young Balkan country, full of imposing mountains, lakes of crystal-clear water, original villages and centuries-old customs. Nevertheless, Northern Macedonia, which borders Serbia in the north and Greece in the south, considered to be one of the poorest countries in Europe.

programme.title: mareTV: The Blue and White Island World of Greece: Mykonos, Naxos and Tinos
programme.desc: Around the once sacred Isle of Delos, some 200 islands, including 20 larger ones, are arranged almost in a circle. This is where the name of the Greek island paradise comes from: Cyclades, a derivation of the Greek word kýklos, circle. Each cyclade has a unique character. The pelican Petros, about 20 years old, is the mascot of Mykonos. He moves from taverna to taverna all day long, scrounging fish. This works out sometimes well and sometimes not so well. Petros does have a few human friends who regularly slip him something, but all too often visitors eager to take pictures block his path. Then he has to "wiggle" his way through the crowd. Jackie Onassis is said to have once brought...

The reason: the resulting waves gnaw at the foundations of the grand palaces. Venetians are very...

programme.title: King of the Mountains - Golden Eagle
programme.desc: Aerial shots of mating Golden eagles, a clash between a Golden and a White-tailed eagle, and an intimate glimpse into their nesting grounds combine to create a spectacular film. Tracking these majestic birds reveals the wild nature of their hunting grounds, showcasing the diverse animal and plant life that share their habitat with the king of the skies. Viewers are brought up close as the eagle effortlessly glides over forests and canyons, abruptly diving in a breathtaking pursuit of prey. Witnessing these birds in their natural habitats is witnessing them at their finest. Embark on a magnificent journey through the skies and landscapes with us.

programme.title: King of the Seas - Sea Eagle
programme.desc: The times where eagles have been seen as varmints are over. They are now perceived as an integral part of the food cycle. Due to the fact that the habitats of the sea eagles in Germany are largely found in the north-eastern regions that are rich in water, the movie accompanies the eagles to an island, home to hundreds of sea ravens, where they rob the baby sea ravens of their food. They seem to always profit from the successes of the fellow creatures in their habitats. This film introduces you to the expert poachers of the animal kingdom.

programme.title: Cuckoo - The Enemy in My Nest
programme.desc: It’s no news that cuckoos are brood parasites: they lay their eggs into the nests of other bird species – a clever trick that spares the rearing of own offspring. Some even go as far as to kill the other chicks in the nest. But why do other parent birds let this happen? Are they too stupid? Too inept? Or simply clueless? Admittedly, cuckoo’s eggs do look deceptively genuine. But the cuckoo chick? Not even remotely! It quickly grows into a giant that looks nothing like its new family. So why don’t the adoptive parents notice the sham then? Until recently, the ornithologists’ theory was: the “victims” have yet to learn to counteract. Turns out: they may even profit from having strangers’...

programme.title: Snowy Owl: Queen of the North
programme.desc: No other owls are capable of surviving the extreme conditions, whereas the snowy owl is able to hunt through six months of bright sunshine and six months of twilight. This film follows a pair of snowy owls as they breed on the tundra of the High Arctic, 300 miles inside the Arctic Circle. Lemming numbers are low this year. Five owlets hatch and they face a struggle if any are going to survive.

programme.title: Hummingbirds: Jewelled Messengers
programme.desc: Hummingbirds live at the limits of what is possible. They have the highest metabolism with a heart rate of 1,200 beats per minute of any vertebrate. Their wings beat 50 times a second. They can hover on the spot, and even fly backwards. To our eyes, they are just a blur. But with the aid of high-speed cameras we can slow down their hyperactive lives and look into their secret world.

programme.title: Moksgmol - The Quest for the Spirit Bear
programme.desc: A forest that lives off fish, a white bear that is not a polar bear, and wolves that feed off the ocean… Canada’s Great Bear Rain Forest is a strange and pristine world, a land that time almost forgot. The awe-inspiring northern coastline of British Columbia with its great fjords that rival those in Norway, is the habitat of numerous species and the scene for the amazing co-existence of wolves, ravens, salmon, bears and a mystical rainforest, whose lives are intricately intertwined…

programme.title: Bear Essentials
programme.desc: We follow three young bears of different species – polar bears, brown bears and sloth bears (like Baloo, the Jungle Book Bear) – that inhabit dramatically varied landscapes as they find their way in the world. We look at how their mothers teach them the skills they need to survive and watch the many dangers they face. Their young lives are full of learning, moments of great tenderness and life-threatening drama. Over three years all of our bears, despite hardships and losses along the way, prove they have what it takes, they all have learned their bear essentials.

programme.title: Search for the Ghost Bears
programme.desc: Our film journey begins in Alaskas west. We are hoping to find glacier bears in the glacial regions of the Katmai National Park on the Douglas River. At the end of July, brown bears have now arrived to fish for salmon. In the surrounding forests, grizzlies look for berries and fresh, green twigs. The Katmai is Alaskas most volcanic area, and with 15 active volcanoes it is a veritable powder keg, surrounded by glaciers. In the Hook glacier region moose and lynx accompany us. Bald eagles have arrived at the glacial boundary and begin to tear apart their freshly caught prey. At last, we catch sight of a glacier bear. Hungry, he has left the ice region and has been forced down here in...

programme.title: Leap Of The Lynx
programme.desc: On the Iberian Peninsula, primeval landscapes are practically non-existent, so the Iberian lynx has lived on cultivated land for centuries – cattle, horse and pig pastures, cork oak forests, timberland, and even holy sites of pilgrimage. The diversity and beauty of these locations are truly stunning and their character and history as relevant to this story as that of the big cat itself. Until five years ago, both populations of Iberian lynx were quickly fading away. Their fragmented habitats were shrinking even further, they were starved by lack of prey and reduced by epidemics. But now, local authorities, scientists, landowners, and other groups have finally begun to act in unison.

programme.title: Secret Life Of Deer
programme.desc: 30 million white-tailed deer live in the United States. They have begun to adapt themselves to living in a world of traffic, pets and backyards. In Cayuga Heights, New York, the suburb’s residents are trying to get used to this exceptional living arrangement. The deer can be spotted daily from kitchen windows and porches. Life in the suburbs is deer heaven – large areas of grass, no predators and plenty of water means their population is on a steady rise. In this documentary, white-tailed deer are outfitted with special cameras to take the viewer into their world. Deercam allows us to see them in a new light – not frozen in the headlights of a car or as shy residents of the woods, but...

programme.title: The Moose Detective
programme.desc: Moose are an iconic species and of great importance to Sweden. That is why the country counts on a very special expert - the moose detective. Recently, a problem has developed on Öland regarding its moose. For a few years now on the island, the moose calves have been dying shortly after birth. Its a mystery. Every effort is made to save them. The island has called upon the moose detective to investigate. He follows several leads. Soon one of the suspects is identified - climate change. But it is not easy to convict the culprit. There are other suspects as well, the food shortage for example. Maybe they have joined hands as accomplices. In Sweden moose are very important. They are game...

programme.title: The Beavers are back
programme.desc: The return of the beavers is one of the greatest success stories of nature conservation in Germany. Hunted for a long time and almost exterminated, today more than 35.000 beavers live in Germany again – and the trend is rising. But how did this happen? One gets to see the mostly nocturnal animals only rarely. Klaus WeiSSmann has spent more than two years tracking down the shy beavers and documenting their spread in Germany. Which ways do they use? What dangers are they exposed to? Step by step, this film tells the exciting and sometimes odd success story of the likeable rodents.

programme.title: Rewilding: Back to Nature
programme.desc: Worldwide, there are various projects and approaches to give nature more space again. The aim is to create larger wilderness areas that develop with hardly any influence of humans - by reintroducing so-called key animal species and creating a network of wilderness corridors across entire continents. Rewilding promises to be a cost-effective form of conservation in which we can boost biodiversity and protect the climate.

programme.title: The Secret of Migrating Birds - Tryst at the Red Sea
programme.desc: Each year in spring, Israel witnesses a unique spectacle. Many millions of migrating birds cross the land bridge between Africa, Asia and Europe.Their first major roosting place after an exhausting nonstop flight over the African deserts is in southern Israel – a vital stopover. Here they replenish their energy reserves. The flocks of migrating birds are pursued by flocks of ornithologists. Hundreds of birders flood into the port city of Eilat on the Red Sea to take part in the Migration Festival. For a week, Israels southernmost coastal resort is home to international scientists and amateur birders.

programme.title: Wild Bavaria
programme.desc: The moon disappears behind the horizon and the stage is set for a new day in the Alps of Berchtesgaden.

programme.title: Wild Bavaria
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Bavaria - In The Shadow of the Watzmann.
programme.desc: Mighty and mysterious, King Watzmann sits above Germanys only alpine national park.

programme.title: Wilderness in Europe: The Bohemian Forest
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Psychogramm of a Spiritual Landscape
programme.desc: The Bohemian Forest is the source of the Vltava River, home to primeval forests, untouched high moors and bubbling torrents. This archaic stretch of land, which includes the Bavarian Forest, was long considered impenetrable and mysterious. Since the fall of the Iron Curtain, Bavarian border residents have rediscovered new references to this unusual forest landscape for themselves. This is also the case with photo artist Bastian Kalous, who has been documenting his homeland for years with nostalgic-looking Polaroid photographs and is dealing with its eventful history for an illustrated book. Or Elisa Belotti and Marco Heurich, who have dedicated their lives to the lynxes. In order for...

programme.title: I Got a Monster: Americas Most Corrupt Police Squad
programme.desc: Retells in highly dramatic fashion one of the USAs biggest police corruption scandals. In 2017, Baltimore was rocked by the Federal indictment of Wayne Jenkins, a highly decorated supercop and leader of the Baltimore Police Departments elite Gun Trace Task Force along with six other members on racketeering charges.

programme.title: OJ25
programme.desc: The bombshell of "The Fuhrman Tapes" takes an odd twist when comments on the tapes about Judge Itos wife lead the prosecution to try to have the judge removed from the case.

programme.title: OJ25
programme.desc: Famed medical examiner Dr. Henry Lee takes the stand for the defense and takes issue with how evidence was collected at the crime scene.

programme.title: Judgment With Ashleigh Banfield
programme.sub-title: S01 : E25 Judgment With Ashleigh Banfield
programme.desc: For the four LAPD cops who beat Rodney King with batons it may have been business as usual. But then the world learned that it had been captured on video, and those 81 seconds changed everything.

programme.title: Judgment With Ashleigh Banfield
programme.sub-title: S01 : E26 Judgment With Ashleigh Banfield
programme.desc: When Charlie Manson and members of his "family" were given the death penalty for the Helter Skelter murders, people thought their reign of terror was over. But then California overturned the death penalty, making parole an option and allowing Manson to once again take center stage.

programme.title: 72 Hours: True Crime
programme.desc: 19 year old Greg Parsons is convicted of brutally murdering his mother mainly on evidence of the audio tape of a song hed written, "Kill your Parents".

programme.title: 72 Hours: True Crime
programme.desc: In Whistler B.C., a winter wonderland for the rich and trendy, three people meet: the son of a wealthy Frenchman, a Vancouver businessman looking for investors and a real estate agent trying to sell a mountainside estate; one of them is a con man.

programme.title: 72 Hours: True Crime
programme.desc: In 2002, several bank robberies take place; all of them link to an overweight man; but when his identity is eventually revealed, it is a huge surprise for all.

programme.title: 72 Hours: True Crime
programme.desc: A woman is told by a friend that she was a passenger in a car where she was confronted with a guys head in a bucket.

programme.title: OJ25
programme.desc: The defense unleashes a bombshell. The say they have a tape of Detective Mark Fuhrman using the N-Word. Repeatedly. The question is, will the jury be allowed to hear it?

programme.title: OJ25
programme.desc: Detective Mark Fuhrman is called to account for an audiotape of him using the N-word and when the jury hears the tape Fuhrman takes the fifth rather than explain himself.

programme.title: Judgment With Ashleigh Banfield
programme.sub-title: S01 : E27 Judgment With Ashleigh Banfield
programme.desc: Just weeks after a jury found four LAPD officers innocent of brutally beating Rodney King, the LAPD was once again put in the spotlight for all the wrong reasons.

programme.title: Judgment With Ashleigh Banfield
programme.sub-title: S01 : E28 Judgment With Ashleigh Banfield
programme.desc: Prosecutors said the death of 16-year-old Neil Beagley was completely preventable; so much so his parents were charged with criminally negligent homicide.

programme.title: Someone They Knew... With Tamron Hall
programme.sub-title: S02 : E03 Someone They Knew... With Tamron Hall
programme.desc: When Atlanta homemaker Sara Tokars is kidnapped, shot, and killed in front of her two young children, police are baffled. Who would want her dead?

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Night of Horror at Devils Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case) - On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her little sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Mysterious Murder at the Farm (Valerie Bary Case)- On Friday, March 26, 2004, in the region of Dijon, Laurent Bary came home from his work to discover the lifeless body of his wife, Valerie, bathing in a pool of blood. According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. A maniac inspired by a horror movie? Investigators soon find that the young girl felt she was being watched, and even threatened...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

An unusual investigation that leads the police down a number of false avenues.

programme.desc: Arriving at her work, the secretary of a small firm in the suburbs of Geneva finds the body of Jean-Raymond Blatti, the companys new accountant. Over the course of the investigation, this inscription will appear as one of the many mysteries of this case which is particularly rich in twists and turns.

programme.title: Sommarminnen
programme.desc: Helène ar familjens matriark, och har agnat sitt liv åt att samla konst och antikviteter. Nar hennes liv till slut kommer till anda står hennes tre barn med ett stort arv i form av ett vackert gammalt lantgods och allt det huserar, men de ar allt annat an overens om hur dessa slaktklenoder ska forvaltas. Sommarminnen ar Guldpalmsvinnaren Olivier Assayas starka familjedrama med Juliette Binoche, Charles Berling och Jeremie Renier.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: The Dresser
programme.desc: En odesdiger natt på en liten engelsk teater under andra varldskriget, satter en trupp med kringresande skådespelare upp Shakespeares "King Lear".

programme.title: Rabbit-Proof Fence
programme.desc: Tre piger – halvt hvide, halvt aboriginere – skal skoles til at arbejde for hvide familier og derefter havne i en sammenhæng, hvor de med tiden kan gifte sig med hvide mænd. Men pigerne beslutter at flygte, og de følger det over 1500 kilometer lange hegn langs statsgrænsen på et omvæltende eventyr i den australske vildmark.

programme.title: Jimmy P.
programme.desc: En orolig indianveteran bildar en exceptionell vanskap med en fransk psykoanalytiker nar de forsoker hitta botemedel mot deras lidande.

programme.title: The Dark Divide
programme.desc: En dramakomedi som baserar sig på verkliga handelser, med David Cross - som vi sett i serien Arrested Development, och Debra Messing - kand från serien Will and Grace, i huvudrollerna. Robert ar en fjarilsforskare vars fru insjuknar i cancer. Frun overtalar sin uppgivne man att åka på en fjarilsresa, vars ovantade moten och forvantade motgångar oppnar Roberts ogon på nytt.

programme.title: Shattered Glass
programme.desc: Hayden Christensen spelar huvudrollen i denna kritikerrosade berattelse om en utskamd journalist, regisserad och samskriven av Billy Ray, Oscar®-nominerad forfattare av KAPTEN PHILLIPS. Nar den beromda journalisten Stephen Glass (Christensen) plotsligt utredas av en Forbes.com-reporter (Steve Zahn) avslojar sokandet att Glass har diktat ihop många av sina sensationella berattelser, vilket leder till hans ultimata fall i detta gripande, faktabaserade drama.

programme.title: K-19: The Widowmaker
programme.desc: 1961 inleder Sovjetunionens forsta karnvapenbarande ubåt på sin jungfruresa i Nordatlanten. Men ubåten fungerar inte optimalt, och når det uppstår fel med karnreaktorn har den katastrofala konsekvenser for besattningen. Tillsammans måste besattningen kampa for att undvika en karnkatastrof som både ar livshotande och kan starta ett nytt varldskrig mellan de två supermakterna.

programme.title: Amores Perros
programme.desc: Karlek ar många saker — vissa bra, andra dåliga — men framfor allt suger den. En fruktansvard bilolycka binder samman tre berattelser, var och en med karaktarer som hanterar forlust, ånger och livets hårda verkligheter, allt i karlekens namn.

programme.title: The Crying Game
programme.desc: Den brittiska soldaten Jody kidnappas av IRA, men bildar ett ovantat vanskapsband med sin vakt Fergus. Nar villkoren de satt upp for Jodys frigivning inte mots, faller uppgiften att avratta honom på just Fergus, en uppgift Fergus får svårt att genomfora. På flykt från IRA inleder Fergus ett nytt liv i London, dar Jodys tidigare liv kommer att forma honom. The Crying Game ar ett Oscarsvinnande romantiskt kriminaldrama med Forest Whitaker, Stephen Rea och Jaye Davidson.

programme.title: Man on Fire
programme.desc: MAN ON FIRE ar en gripande thriller med Oscar® belonade Denzel Washington i huvudrollen. Han spelar Creasy, en f.d. utbrand CIA agent som tappat livsgnistan. Creasy overtalas av sin van Rayburn (Christopher Walken) att skydda en tioårig flicka i Mexico City dar barnkidnappningar tillhor vardagen. Creasy kommer flickan nara och deras relation gor att han återfår viljan att leva. Nar hon sedan blir kidnappad tappar Creasy allt forstånd. Han ger sig ut på en vansinnesjakt for att finna henne och ingenting kan stoppa honom.

programme.title: The Good Heart
programme.desc: Jaques (Brian Cox – THE BOURNE IDENTITY) ager en sjaskig bar, som fungerar som ett andra hem for en brokig skara professionella drinkare. Jaques sjalv ar fast besluten att supa och roka sig till dods. Nar han moter den unge hemlose Lucas (Paul Dano – THERE WILL BE BLOOD), som också gett upp hoppet om livet, tycker han sig ha hittat den perfekte arvingen till baren. Jaques borjar lara Lucas sitt kungadomes manschauvernistiska lagar: inga nya kunder, ingen personlig kontakt med gasterna, och absolut inga kvinnor! Lucas lar sig fort, men vanskapen satts på prov då den olyckliga och vackra April (Isild Le Besco) soker skydd i baren.

programme.title: K-19: The Widowmaker
programme.desc: 1961 inleder Sovjetunionens forsta karnvapenbarande ubåt på sin jungfruresa i Nordatlanten. Men ubåten fungerar inte optimalt, och når det uppstår fel med karnreaktorn har den katastrofala konsekvenser for besattningen. Tillsammans måste besattningen kampa for att undvika en karnkatastrof som både ar livshotande och kan starta ett nytt varldskrig mellan de två supermakterna.

programme.title: Dinner Rush
programme.desc: Dinner Rush utspelar sig under vad som från borjan inte tycks vara något annat an en helt vanlig jaktig kvall på Louis Cropas (Danny Aiello) populara restaurang Gigino i det fashionabla TriBeCa-kvarteret i New York. En gång var trattorian en enkel familjerestaurang men nu har den forvandlats till kvarterets mesta innekrog, stallet dar alla vill bli sedda. Detta mycket tack vare krogaren Cropas son Udos (Edoardo Ballerini) innovativa matlagningskonst som kommit att bli stallets kannetecken. Och just den har kvallen ar restaurangen som ett kalejdoskop av livet i dagens New York...

programme.title: Boys on the Side
programme.desc: Tre kvinnor begår av misstag ett brott och tvingas på flykt i denna komedi. Under resans gång utveckla något de aldrig riktigt kant tidigare: en kansla av tillhorighet och vanskap.

programme.title: Gringa
programme.desc: En olycklig tonårstjej rymmer till Mexiko for att hitta den pappa hon aldrig kant. Tillsammans lar de sig att en familj kan bli hel igen, aven om de bara har de bitar som saknas.

programme.title: Birdman
programme.desc: I den omtalade och kritikerhyllade svarta komedin BIRDMAN eller The Unexpected Virtue of Ignorance ser vi Michael Keaton i huvudrollen som en skådespelare, mest kand for att ha spelat den ikoniska superhjalten Birdman. Han ska nu regissera en teateruppforestallning på Broadway och vi får folja honom under de hektiska dagarna innan den stora premiarkvallen. Samtidigt som han slåss mot sina inre demoner och sitt stora ego så forsoker han lappa ihop både familj och karriar. For regi står Alejandro G. Iñárritu (BABEL, ÄLSKADE HUNDAR) och i ovriga roller ser vi bl.a. Zach Galifianakis, Edward Norton, Emma Stone, Naomi Watts.

programme.title: Ljus i skymningen (Lights in the Dusk)
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om nattvakten Koistinen som forlorar jobbet, friheten och drommarna. Men till sist skonjer han en strimma hopp.

programme.title: Varg
programme.desc: Varg ar en storslagen film om Klemens (Peter Stormare) och hans systerson Nejla som lever mitt i det norrlandska landskapet på gransen mellan Sverige och Norge.

programme.title: In Tranzit
programme.desc: Baserad på en sann historia. I chockvågorna efter andra varldskriget, under den kalla vintern 1946, skickas av misstag en grupp tyska krigsfångar till ett ryskt kvinnofånglager som styrs av kvinnliga fångvaktare. Fångvaktarna, som forlorat många narstående på grund av Nazisternas brutalitet, mottar de nyanlanda fångarna med stor fientlighet och ser en mojlighet till hamnd...

programme.title: Winged Creatures
programme.desc: På ett ogonblick forandras allt - hur går du vidare nar ditt liv slås i spillror? Det ar tidig morgon i Los Angeles, en psykopat skjuter besinningslost ihjal ett antal oskyldiga manniskor på en frukostservering... Hur reagerar de som overlever eller de anhoriga till de som mordats av en slump?

programme.title: Black Coal, Thin Ice
programme.desc: På en kolfabrik liksom vid en soptipp, i olika andar av provinsen Heilongjian, påtraffas delar från samma kropp. En man har styckats och spridits ut, på ett avstånd for stort for en ensam garningsman. Zhang Zili (spelad av Liao Fan, som belonades for basta skådespelarinsats i Berlin) åtar sig fallet, men under ett misslyckat ingripande blir två av hans kollegor skjutna och Zhang tvingas lamna sin tjanst. Fem år senare blir Zhang uppsokt av sin forne kollega. Ett dubbelmord, identiskt med det som agde rum 1999, har skett och Zhang får chansen till återupprattelse.

programme.title: Once Were Warriors
programme.desc: Hos familjen Heke finns ingen frid att tala om. Jake Heke blir våldsam nar han dricker, den ena sonen har gått med i ett gatugang och den andra står infor åtal. Mamman Beth och barnen står infor det svåra, men livsavgorande valet mellan att stanna kvar i en hopplos situation, och att slå sig fria. Once Were Warriors ar ett prisvinnande familjedrama om att bejaka sitt forflutna for att skapa sin framtid.

programme.title: Anna and the Apocalypse
programme.desc: Julpynt och bjallerklang, musikalsång och zombieapokalyps. Mitt i julstoket hotas småstaden Little Haven av en plotsligt annalkande undergång. Anna och hennes vanner bestammer sig for att bekampa zombiehorderna – men vem kan man lita på i en varld som faller samman? En skrackkomedi i musikalskrud i juletid.

programme.title: This is England 88 (Part 1)
programme.desc: De forodande handelser som agde rum for 18 månader sedan hemsoker Lol (Vicky McClure) och Woody (Joe Gilgun), som båda kampar med att overkomma det kanslomassiga nederlaget. Lol inser snabbt att hennes kraftreserver sinar nar hon kampar med att ta sig an nya ansvar och gamla forpliktelser. Tillsammans med sin sjalsfrande Woody, fortvivlad over sitt svek och sitt sjalvvalda exil från ganget, blir Lol annu mer isolerad och ensam.

programme.title: Sander jul
programme.desc: Nar hennes on-air-partner bestammer sig for att lamna Amerikas favoritmorgonprogram, meddelar Veronika Daniels att hon kommer att valja sin nya medvard bland en handfull kandidater som inkluderar Charlie Fisher, en lokal nyhetsupplasare i NY.

programme.title: A Merry Holiday
programme.desc: Christy, en mycket framgångsrik forsaljare stressar over att landa en stor affar. Till sin hjalp tar hon medarbetaren Jonathan som ar upptagen med att pynta sin ungkarlslya till ett magiskt vinterland for att impa på flickvannens pappa. De kommer båda i klinch med varann, men inser att de måste samarbeta och hjalpa varandra. Ju mer tid de spenderar, desto avslappnat blir relationen dem emellan och kanske ar det inte bara jobbet som for dem samman langre?

programme.title: Tyler Perrys a Madea Christmas
programme.desc: Madea sprider sin alldeles egen unika julstamning nar hon blir overtalad att spendera julen ute på landet med en van och hennes familj.

programme.title: Deck the Halls
programme.desc: Den har deckaren baseras på boken av den bastsaljande mysterieforfattaren Mary Higgins Clark. En kvinnlig detektiv slår sig samman med en amatordetektiv for att hitta sin forsvunna pappa.

programme.title: My Christmas Inn
programme.desc: Nar affarskvinnan Jennifer får reda på att hennes foraldrar tanker resa bort over julen utan henne, bestammer hon sig for att lamna sitt hektiska storstadsliv i San Francisco for att besoka Grandmas Inn i Alaska, ett vardshus som hon har arvt for att renovera och sedan salja.

programme.title: Love The Coopers
programme.desc: Nar fyra generationer av Cooper-klanen samlas for att fira jul tillsammans så blir foljden att en rad minst sagt ovantade gaster och en radda helt osannolika handelser vander upp och ner på kvallen – och familjens medlemmar bjuds på en handelserik resa som går mot en gladjande återupptackt av familjebandens och karlekens magi. Diane Keaton, Alan Arkin och Marisa Tomei gor tillsammans med John Goodman, Ed Helms, Amanda Seyfried och Olivia Wilde fantastiska rolltolkningar i denna hysteriskt roliga och hjartevarmande komedi.

programme.title: A Winter Princess
programme.desc: Efter en prestigefull gala bestammer sig prinsessan Carly for att ta ett sabbatsår och hoppa på ett for henne dromjobb vid en skidanlaggning. Ingen av hennes nya arbetskamrater kanner till hennes ratta identitet, men nar medlemmar från den kungliga slakten borjar dyka upp vid anlaggningen blir det plotsligt valdigt komplicerat att hålla på hemligheten utan att bli upptackt. Allt medan de preppar for ett 50års jubileum av anlaggningen, och Carly som borjar bli stortkar i agarens bror Jesse. Carly står nu infor stora vagval i livet och kanner sig bara alltmer forvirrad ju langre tiden går…

programme.title: Another Christmas Coincedence
programme.desc: Alice och Jack, två framlingar med totalt olika bakgrunder hamnar av en slump en helg på samma brollop. Det klickar direkt mellan dem men Alice ar tveksam till en ny relation efter ett havererat långdistansforhållande. Uppmuntrad av mamma Olga borjar Alice sakta vanja sig med tanken och borja dejta igen. Mer tillfalligheterna for dem narmare samtidigt som nya hinder avloser varann och utmanar den nyfunna romansen.

programme.title: Vilken tomte?
programme.desc: Den riktige jultomten tumlar ut ur sin slade och får minnesforlust. Han traffar snart en utsliten tv-reporter som ar hans enda hopp till att få minnet tillbaka i tid for att radda julen.

programme.title: Silent Night: A Song for the World
programme.desc: Stilla natt, heliga natt - Joseph Mohrs heroiska resa 1818, nar han skapade varldens mest kanda julsång. Den sanna historien om låten berattas som en fiktiv historia.

programme.title: Anna and the Apocalypse

Anna och hennes vanner bestammer sig for att bekampa zombiehorderna – men vem kan man lita på i en varld som faller samman? En skrackkomedi i musikalskrud i juletid.

programme.title: The Loss Adjuster
programme.desc: En forsakringsman som kampar med forlust och karlek upptacker nya mojligheter under en vecka full av ovantade handelser och komiska vandpunkter.

programme.desc: De forodande handelser som agde rum for 18 månader sedan hemsoker Lol (Vicky McClure) och Woody (Joe Gilgun), som båda kampar med att overkomma det kanslomassiga nederlaget. Lol inser snabbt att hennes kraftreserver sinar nar hon kampar med att ta sig an nya ansvar och gamla forpliktelser. Tillsammans med sin sjalsfrande Woody, fortvivlad over sitt svek och sitt sjalvvalda exil från ganget, blir Lol annu mer isolerad och ensam.

programme.title: Just Friends
programme.desc: Får vi presentera Chris Bander. Highschool på nittiotalet var en pina: han var blyg, overviktig och hemligt foralskad i Jamie, hans enda kompis och tillika en av skolans mest populara hejarklacksledare. Men nar han antligen hade lyckats samla mod nog att gora en framstot, ville hon bara att de skulle vara vanner! I dag ar Chris en aslacker skivproducent i LA och kan valja bland en uppsjo av vackra och villiga tjejer. Och nar han plotsligt blir strandsatt i sin gamla hemstad ser han chansen att forfora Jamie en gång och for alla. Men det ar nu inte så latt att ta steget från att vara "bara vanner" till att bli "knullkompisar".

programme.title: Jul på bestallning
programme.desc: Gretchen får julen att handa var som helst och nar som helst.

programme.title: Love The Coopers
programme.desc: Nar fyra generationer av Cooper-klanen samlas for att fira jul tillsammans så blir foljden att en rad minst sagt ovantade gaster och en radda helt osannolika handelser vander upp och ner på kvallen – och familjens medlemmar bjuds på en handelserik resa som går mot en gladjande återupptackt av familjebandens och karlekens magi. Diane Keaton, Alan Arkin och Marisa Tomei gor tillsammans med John Goodman, Ed Helms, Amanda Seyfried och Olivia Wilde fantastiska rolltolkningar i denna hysteriskt roliga och hjartevarmande komedi.

programme.title: 12 Gifts of Christmas
programme.desc: Nar Anna, en arbetslos konstnar, inte får ihop ekonomin, anlitas hon som personal jul-shopper åt Marc, en spand bolagschef.

programme.title: Julens Underland
programme.desc: Jultiden i NYC ar allt annat an underbar for den kampande artisten Heidi Neill.

programme.title: So This Is Christmas
programme.desc: Unga Ashley håller på att kora i diket med sitt liv och hanger ute med helt fel personer i forsok att fly undan allt familjedrama. Plotsligt verkar allt byta riktning då hantverkaren de anlitat uppmuntrar henne att satta upp en jul pjas for opriviligerade ungdomar. Ashley ser sin chans att heala sin egen problemfyllda familj genom att uppmuntra andra i battre behov av hjalp. Tillsammans upptacker de fantastiska av vad man enkelt kan åstakomma genom den underbara gåvan att bara kunna ge till andra.

programme.title: A Merry Holiday
programme.desc: Christy, en mycket framgångsrik forsaljare stressar over att landa en stor affar. Till sin hjalp tar hon medarbetaren Jonathan som ar upptagen med att pynta sin ungkarlslya till ett magiskt vinterland for att impa på flickvannens pappa. De kommer båda i klinch med varann, men inser att de måste samarbeta och hjalpa varandra. Ju mer tid de spenderar, desto avslappnat blir relationen dem emellan och kanske ar det inte bara jobbet som for dem samman langre?

programme.title: A Winter Princess
programme.desc: Efter en prestigefull gala bestammer sig prinsessan Carly for att ta ett sabbatsår och hoppa på ett for henne dromjobb vid en skidanlaggning. Ingen av hennes nya arbetskamrater kanner till hennes ratta identitet, men nar medlemmar från den kungliga slakten borjar dyka upp vid anlaggningen blir det plotsligt valdigt komplicerat att hålla på hemligheten utan att bli upptackt. Allt medan de preppar for ett 50års jubileum av anlaggningen, och Carly som borjar bli stortkar i agarens bror Jesse. Carly står nu infor stora vagval i livet och kanner sig bara alltmer forvirrad ju langre tiden går…

programme.title: 12 Pups of Christmas
programme.desc: Erin har precis avslutat ett forhållande och laddar for omstart med nytt jobb i en ny stad. Men just nar hon trodde att hon landat springer hon på den sjalvcentriske bossen Martin. Han kampar med att hålla sitt foretag vid liv och ber Erin om hjalp att ta hand om 12st valpar som lamnats kvar efter ett jobb precis lagom innan jul. Ju mer de jobbar med varann strommar kanslorna fram och karlek uppstår just lagom till den stundande hogtiden.

programme.title: Christmas Land
programme.desc: Christmas Land har sett battre dagar sedan Glindas tragiska bortgång och Jules tvingas ta många komplicerade beslut.

programme.title: Nothing Like the Holidays
programme.desc: De avlagsna medlemmarna i familjen Rodriguez samlas i sina foraldrars hem for att fira vad som kan vara deras sista jul tillsammans i denna hjartevarmande julkomedi.

programme.title: Anna and the Apocalypse
programme.desc: Julpynt och bjallerklang, musikalsång och zombieapokalyps. Mitt i julstoket hotas småstaden Little Haven av en plotsligt annalkande undergång. Anna och hennes vanner bestammer sig for att bekampa zombiehorderna – men vem kan man lita på i en varld som faller samman? En skrackkomedi i musikalskrud i juletid.

programme.title: Just Friends
programme.desc: Får vi presentera Chris Bander. Highschool på nittiotalet var en pina: han var blyg, overviktig och hemligt foralskad i Jamie, hans enda kompis och tillika en av skolans mest populara hejarklacksledare. Men nar han antligen hade lyckats samla mod nog att gora en framstot, ville hon bara att de skulle vara vanner! I dag ar Chris en aslacker skivproducent i LA och kan valja bland en uppsjo av vackra och villiga tjejer. Och nar han plotsligt blir strandsatt i sin gamla hemstad ser han chansen att forfora Jamie en gång och for alla. Men det ar nu inte så latt att ta steget från att vara "bara vanner" till att bli "knullkompisar".

programme.title: This is England 88 (Part 3)
programme.desc: De forodande handelser som agde rum for 18 månader sedan hemsoker Lol (Vicky McClure) och Woody (Joe Gilgun), som båda kampar med att overkomma det kanslomassiga nederlaget. Lol inser snabbt att hennes kraftreserver sinar nar hon kampar med att ta sig an nya ansvar och gamla forpliktelser. Tillsammans med sin sjalsfrande Woody, fortvivlad over sitt svek och sitt sjalvvalda exil från ganget, blir Lol annu mer isolerad och ensam.

programme.title: Happy New Year, Colin Burstead
programme.desc: Colin Burstead bestammer sig for att hyra en påkostad herrgård for att fira in det nya året med familj och slaktingar. Nar hans oinbjudna bror David dyker upp, stalls rivaliteten mellan dem på sin spets. Nyårsfirandet som Colin hade hoppats bli en dramafri sammanslutning med familjen, blir istallet bli en uppslutning av intriger. Happy New Year, Colin Burstead ar den senaste filmen från kritikerfavoriten Ben Wheatley, genomsyrad av hans karakteristiska morka humor och okonventionella berattande.

programme.title: Guess Whos Coming To Christmas Dinner?
programme.desc: Den aktivistiska, liberala och progressiva juridikstudenten Maya tar med sin nya pojkvan hem for julen utan att beratta for familjen att han ar vit. Gissa vem som kommer till julmiddag?

programme.desc: Chef Spencer starts this spicy barbeque episode with flavours from Thailand with a Bok Choy with a Ginger Chili Sauce. Powerful birds eye chilies are packed into a sweet and spicy sauce and served over tasty grilled bok choy. Spencer then introduces us to Calabrian chilies, mashed into a spice paste and rubbed on butterflied chicken that then gets grilled to flame-kissed perfection. Next, Spencer gives fresh calamari some heat with Korean chilies that add their distinctive heat and flavour before grilling this scrumptious recipe and serving it over a comforting bed of rice and peas. Finally, Spencer prepares Seekh Kabobs, made with ground lamb spiked with punchy dried Kashmiri chilies...

The rotisserie does the heavy lifting for Mr. Watts whole roast chicken - spiked with bright Spanish flavours like Spanish chilies and smoked paprika, slow cooked and served extra juicy. programme.title: Eggplant

programme.title: Fast Food Barbecue

programme.title: The Last Crusade of Indiana Terry
programme.sub-title: S04 : E01 Hollywood Weapons: Fact or Fiction? S4 - "The Last Crusade of Indiana Terry"
programme.desc: Terry channels his inner Dr. Jones and tests 1 scene from Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade containing 3 different tests, two of which they will need a tank for. The duo will travel down to Uvalde, TX to visit Drivetanks.com to see if a tank round will topple over a car, and if a 9mm round can travel through three Germans.

programme.title: Equalizing Terry
programme.sub-title: S04 : E02 Hollywood Weapons: Fact or Fiction? S4 - "Equalizing Terry"
programme.desc: Terry and Larry will test 3 scenes from Denzel Washington’s Equalizer films. Can Terry be as cool as Denzel and use propane tanks and a microwave to create an explosion, use a staple gun to take out the bad guy, or create a scenario where a flash bang will ignite a room full of baking flour?

programme.title: Under Fire
programme.desc: The drought conditions in Montana threaten to close down hunting and fishing in the Treasure State. But dead fish and restrictions are the least of the Wardens worries when the Bears come to town.

programme.title: The Crash
programme.sub-title: S02 : E01 The Flying Kestrel S2 - "The Crash"
programme.desc: After driver Jon Webster crashes the Flying Kestrel at 148 mph, the team must work out what went wrong and have to decide if the dream of a land speed record is worth risking it all?

programme.title: India: Can Kolkata be considered a foodie destination of India?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Maximum Foodie S1 - "India: Can Kolkata be considered a foodie destination of India?"
programme.desc: Liesel pinballs around a city known for its gastronomy, the forgotten hub of British East India trading company, Kolkata. From trying out what the bustling city’s vibrant street food scene has to offer, to the lesser known gems, including, venturing into India’s only Chinatown and sampling their delicacies. A tale of walking food tours, hole in the wall joints serving up North Eastern dumplings, messy fish markets, and of course, the pride of Bengal, the Hilsa fish. Is Kolkata up to par with the other major metropolitan cities of India? This episode finds out exactly that!

programme.title: Nevada: What else is there in Nevada for foodies besides Vegas?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Nevada: What else is there in Nevada for foodies besides Vegas?"
programme.desc: This investigative mission starts off in the sin city atmosphere of the Vegas strip. After a gluttonous stint at a generic buffet, Liesel is inspired to do a road trip to find iconic gems in the state of Nevada. From ghost towns, to monstrous foodie challenges, to hole in the wall dive bars in the middle of nowhere, this trip has it all. Liesel finds the resurgence of Basque cuisine in Northern Nevada, and learns that Reno can do fine dining as well! A trip to Virginia city also reveals that the Silver State has some haunted bars where patrons from the 1800s are rumored to be still imbibing and spooking locals! It’s a road trip in every sense of the word!

programme.title: New Zealand and Australia
programme.sub-title: S01 : E11 Travel Quest S1 - "New Zealand and Australia"
programme.desc: Bill has always been fascinated with the Americas Cup yacht racing – it’s as intense as the name implies. But the big adventure is riding in, and then flying, a Soviet Mig Jet doing stunts and mind numbing close fly-bys.

programme.title: Kenyas Great Grasslands
programme.sub-title: S01 : E12 Travel Quest S1 - "Kenyas Great Grasslands"
programme.desc: Bicycling is a safe and leisurely activity, until you decide to do it through the wilderness of Kenya with large lion, elephant and buffalo populations.

programme.title: Russia
programme.desc: Jonathan faces his toughest challenge yet as he enters a country that has been coming to grips in defining and understanding their own cuisine. Through the historical turmoil and harsh climate, Russia has lost it’s traditional way of cooking, and eating. But the country is reviving this culture; Jonathan ventures the far stretches of the country to learn about modern cooks, as well as ancient kitchens housing the one key tool that gave birth to true Russian cuisine, the Russian oven. He’ll learn their insights, understand their efforts, and work with traditional Russian ingredients to learn what the cuisine used to be, and where it’s headed today.

programme.title: Rome: What are the tourists missing out on?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Rome: What are the tourists missing out on?"
programme.desc: Italy is a vacationer’s paradise. The food, the people, the sights and sounds, the history! But are the tourists doing it right when it comes to the trying out authentic food in Rome? Liesel embarks on a mission to explore the street food of the city. With the help of her food journalist buddy, Saverio de Luca, Liesel sifts through pasticceri, food festivals, touristed hotspots, all in an effort to understand real Roman food.

programme.title: Emlia Romagna: What’s the food like?
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Maximum Foodie S1 - "Emlia Romagna: What’s the food like?"
programme.desc: The region of Emilia Romagna is lush with gentle rolling hills where time honored ingredients like truffles, olives, and vast vineyards can be found. But this region is usually overshadowed by it’s more famous neighboring cities, Florence and Venice. To understand the food of this region, Liesel explores the quaint sea-side town of Rimini and the hugely impressive Bologna. Its a tale of discovering local foodie passion that allows Liesel to hunt for truffles and try her hand in making her own gelato, a the world’s only Gelato University!
